ongside your newfound AI companion, Grace. <br></li><li>Get that <strong>classic Sega Genesis and Super Nintendo feel</strong> with beautiful graphics, a unique mechanic, and a killer soundtrack.<br></li><li>Jump straight into the action - no long, drawn-out tutorials in this laboratory.</li></ul>",
